---
title: Sesame-Crusted Salmon Poke Bowl with Rice & Ponzu Slaw
description: Finish off the day feeling rejuvenated with a salmon poke bowl. Nourishing for the body and soul, the salmon is seasoned with sweet and soy flavours that pop against the fluffy rice. It’s a breath of fresh air in a bowl.

